{"tid":2180982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"安倍辭職   專家：日與美聯手為開戰作準備","createTime":"2020-08-30T09:22:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T09:35:14.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c7ec9bdfde092fd4dd24e0e4a3160a18a124a6e9","tid":2180982,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T09:22:20.000Z","msg":"日本首相安倍晉三28日舉行記者會表示，8月上旬確認舊疾潰瘍性大腸炎復發，決定請辭首相。對此，總體經濟學者吳嘉隆昨在臉書表示，「安倍因病辭職，會影響到美日關係，也會影響到台灣」。今（30）日吳嘉隆更分析安倍用意，表示「確保自己的親美抗中路線，得以在明年之後延續下去￼￼￼！這才是他辭職的真正意思」。更說「日本的提前一年改組，等同於提前完成準備，會與美國聯手來準備對中共的開戰。」....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=805864\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D805864&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=97be214d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D805864&h=9ea4f3bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=805864</a>"},{"pid":"8899a42164edfcbc4947308b53674380834a3ee8","tid":2180982,"uid":17799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T09:35:14.000Z","msg":"真係打再call我"}]}